- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The approach uses monocular images to train the UAV, which involves computer vision techniques.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The approach uses reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of AI.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The approach involves end-to-end deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with controlling a UAV in a real environment, which falls under the domain of systems and control.
